name: Hana
description: Hana (HANA) is a meme cryptocurrency token on the Ethereum blockchain launched in September 2024. It was taken over by the community and is currently community driven. HANA token is structured to be user-friendly, featuring no buy or sell tax fee, making it accessible for a wide range of traders. Hana, a popular Japanese dog, symbolizes not just a new token but a piece of crypto history reimagined.
